{"tid":474910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇福錄壽睇到眼濕濕","createTime":"2017-11-20T15:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T01:01:50.000Z","uid":142348,"like":8,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"24d06b25306292efa79c83f8ed22d7348f932621","tid":474910,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"盲屌嘅7頭唔該出一出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前中學星期六有得睇佢真係好撚開心，<br />\n魏仔南扮九姑娘果幕笑到而家<br />\n<br />\n好多人成日話 tvb 月做月差。<br />\n其實係因為冇哂人同冇大眾撐一啲做到野嘅創作人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一睇就知，係佢地三條友嘅高汁要求<br />\n先會做得出咁有心機嘅短劇<br />\n雖然 batman 果度唔知做咩咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw , 其實一睇就睇得出 jolam 係真心好仔<br />\n見獎門人 黯然離場，佢即刻番泥幫拖<br />\n我知實有人話佢撈唔掂先番泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大佬 諗下都知 lan 船都有三斤釘<br />\n起碼有幾億人識佢，做棟篤笑都 zan 度笑啦。<br />\n但佢就係呢個時候番娘家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人 自己都唔撐自己 邊個撐你？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 演藝界從業員，立志復興香港影藝事業<br />\n哪怕係小小 每個人講多句 做多啲<br />\n距離偉大嘅香港復興夢又近一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d330657a046d872e71e68324918b5c9ea5780a66","tid":474910,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"自己留個名先"},{"pid":"a9a5a066b52e3a0fe3add81cef2f6ec422d5c1b4","tid":474910,"uid":73722,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"睇你篇野睇得好辛苦<br />\n利伸中文5"},{"pid":"d126578f4e8d926212d2c402d0bd0b3d0a9d6a01","tid":474910,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"有冇同齡嘅弟兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有回憶"},{"pid":"6c116c13749a4528c969d2c6fbf1d3024c8a37a5","tid":474910,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:10:59.00